text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/james/level1/jamesOnBreakMorning-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>James pushes a plate of slightly misshapen pancakes toward you.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>They were ugly, so they can't go to a customer. Eat them or toss them.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Thanks, James.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Carbs will keep you moving. You'll need it when Vince gets cranky later.<</dialog>`,
