<<dialog "dinerChef">>I'm out of mayo. It's only 2 PM and I am out of mayo. This is a disaster.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Can you buy more nearby?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Vince would rather die than pay retail. We're scraping jars today.<</dialog>`,
