<<dialog "dinerChef">>I shut the grill down in an hour. Anyone orders a burger after that, they get a cold sandwich.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Vince won't like it.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Vince doesn't cook it. I do. Go rest your feet.<</dialog>`,
